title: Kieran Culkin | What's Up, Docs?
description:
Right wing media personalities and their fans are taking the raid of T****’s home pretty hard, while the spike in food prices is prompting the well-to-do to flock to lower priced chains like IHOP and Applebee’s. A working actor since age 6, ‘Succession’ star Kieran Culkin has a knack for learning his lines quickly, which can really get under Brian Cox’s skin. Look for Kieran at this year’s Emmy Awards where he and his co-stars are nominated for a record 14 acting awards!
